326
00:22:14,043 --> 00:22:15,127
Excuse me.

327
00:22:18,672 --> 00:22:19,952
Are you all right?

328
00:22:19,952 --> 00:22:21,960
Y-Yeah.

329
00:22:21,960 --> 00:22:24,136
